<headline>Special Weather Statement issued August 05 at 6:17AM EDT  by NWS NorthernIndiana</headline>
<description>...Patchy Dense Fog Early This Morning...
Patchy dense fog is expected this morning, with visibilities less
than one quarter of a mile possible. If travelling, be alert for
sudden reductions in visibility. If dense fog is encountered, use
your low beams, reduce speed, and increase following distance. Fog
should diminish shortly after sunrise.</description>
